title: What we know so far about the Youtube shooter
text:
What we know so far about the YouTube shooter 12:18pm EDT - 02:10 
An Iranian-born woman who blogged about veganism had accused YouTube of suppressing her videos before she opened fire at the company’s California headquarters, wounding three and killing herself.
